divs: sighting detailsas i was looking in the night sky, in my back yard, i saw 2 dimly white objects moving very slow to the south, my first thought was that they were ufo's the way they moved, it looked like one was following the other or one was higher and one lower, they had no blinking lights on, no sound, and i guess they had the shape of a piece of rice. they moved very slow and it seemed they were moving with hwy 5, by patterson ca, not sure, at the end they looked to angle to the west, towards the hills and i lost sight of them, not because of the hills they just were to far out. i looked at my phone and the time was 10:08 p.m thank you for your time; (name removed) flg cms 07\25\2011 15:56cst
